const Login = () => {
  return (
    <form>
      <input 
      type="text"
      placeholder="Enter Name"
      />
      <input 
      type="password"
      placeholder="Enter Password"
      />
      <Link>
      <input 
      type="submit"
      placeholder="Login"
      />
      </Link>
    </form>
  )
}

export default Login
